The growth of catestrophey bonds has caused changes in the reinsurnace market.  THe rise in the bond market has caused the development of cat bond funds.  \href{http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/818eaa56-f180-11e4-98c5-00144feab7de.html}{FT article} assesses the risk that some of these products are packaging risk into bonds in a similar fashion to CDOs to create bundles of concentrated risk that will damage the industry. 
